<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>Welcome {{ username }}</title>
		<link
			href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
			rel="stylesheet"
			integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<div class="container py-4">
				{{#error}}
				<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
					{{ error }}
				</div>
				{{/error}}

				{{#success}}
				<div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
					{{ success }}
				</div>
				{{/success}}

				<div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-body-tertiary rounded-3 border">
					<div class="container-fluid py-5">
						<h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">
							Welcome <span class="text-danger">{{ username }}</span>
						</h1>
						<p class="fs-4 mb-4">
							In the land of sprockets and wobblywops, the flibberflabbers
							danced merrily under the moonlit sky, their jibber-jabber echoing
							through the gumdrop trees. Meanwhile, the snickerdoodles sang a
							tune only the rainbow snails could hear, while the floppy flippers
							frolicked in the fizzy fountains of fandango.
						</p>
						<a href="{{#isAdmin}}/flag{{/isAdmin}}" {{^isAdmin}}style="pointer-events: none"{{/isAdmin}}>
							<button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="button" {{^isAdmin}}disabled{{/isAdmin}}>
								Get The Flag
							</button>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="row align-items-md-stretch">
					<div class="col-md-6">
						<div class="h-100 p-5 text-bg-dark rounded-3">
							<h2>Add new user</h2>
							<form action="/admin">
								<div class="mb-3">
									<label for="username" class="form-label">Username</label>
									<input
										type="text"
										class="form-control"
										id="username"
										name="username"
										required
									/>
								</div>
								<div class="mb-3">
									<label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
									<input
										type="email"
										class="form-control"
										id="email"
										name="email"
										required
									/>
								</div>
								<div class="mb-3">
									<label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
									<input
										type="password"
										class="form-control"
										id="password"
										name="password"
										required
									/>
								</div>
								<input hidden type="text" name="action" value="addUser" />
								<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-6">
						<div class="h-100 p-5 bg-body-tertiary border rounded-3">
							<h2>Melody of Revelation</h2>
							<p>
								In the vault, behind the red door, lies the secret that can
								change everything. Only those who know the melody can unlock its
								power. The notes are scattered across the city, hidden in plain
								sight. Follow the clues, listen closely, and the truth will
								reveal itself. But beware, for others are also seeking the
								melody, and its meaning may not be what it seems.
							</p>
							<p>
								Rumors swirl around the melody's origin, some claiming it is a
								gift from the heavens, others a creation of ancient alchemy.
								Whispers of its power have reached the ears of the curious and
								the ambitious alike, sparking a race to decipher its tune.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<script
			src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
			integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		></script>
	</body>
</html>
